  "title": "Allow updating the configuration of widgets and allow forcing a render",
  "body": "Goal: be be able to update the hits (or other) widget templates or limit and then force a re-render.\n\n``` js\nhits.updateConfiguration({});\nhits.forceRender();\n```\n\nUse cases:\n- #753 \n- #845 \n\nThis will not be so easy in term of implementation:\n- are every widget worth having those methods?\n- how to do it easily without a lot of boilerplate code?\n",
